caseTitle: Hamza Rasheed Khan v. Election Appellate Tribunal, Lahore High Court, Lahore & others
authorJudge: Mr. Justice Syed Mansoor Ali Shah
tagline: Detailed reasons for holding that Article 62(1)(f) of the Constitution is not a self-executory provision and for overruling Sami Ullah Baloch v. Abdul Karim Nausherwani (PLD 2018 SC 405).
